OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1781608793
OL,3,CIndian national arrested after Russian
OL,4,Cshadow vessel intercepted in Channel
OL,6,FA 38-year-old Indian national has been
OL,7,Farrested after British armed forces
OL,8,Fintercepted a Russian shadow fleet
OL,9,Fvessel in the Channel early on Sunday,
OL,10,Fthe National Crime Agency (NCA) said.
OL,12,FThe Ministry of Defence (MoD) said
OL,13,FRoyal Marine commandos and specially
OL,14,Ftrained law enforcement officers from
OL,15,Fthe NCA boarded a sanctioned oil
OL,16,Ftanker during a six-hour operation `
OL,17,Fthe first UK-led operation of its kind.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
