PN,31702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1781608793
OL,3,CIndian national arrested after Russian
OL,4,Cshadow vessel intercepted in Channel
OL,6,FAccording to the MoD, the operation
OL,7,Fwas supported by aircraft from the
OL,8,FMaritime Air Group (Chinooks, Merlin
OL,9,FMk4 and Wildcat), an RAF P-8 aircraft,
OL,10,FHMS Sutherland and HMS Ledbury.
OL,12,FAn NCA spokesperson said: "Following
OL,13,Fthe interdiction of a Russian shadow
OL,14,Ffleet vessel in the early hours of 14
OL,15,FJune, a 38-year-old Indian national
OL,16,Fhas been arrested by officers from the
OL,17,FNational Crime Agency on suspicion of
OL,18,Fsuspected sanctions offences under the
OL,19,FRussia Regulations.
OL,26,@tD@[OU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1781608793
OL,3,CIndian national arrested after Russian
OL,4,Cshadow vessel intercepted in Channel
OL,6,F"He has been taken into custody where
OL,7,Fhe will be interviewed by NCA
OL,8,Finvestigators. As our investigation
OL,9,Fremains ongoing, we will not be
OL,10,Fcommenting further at this time".
OL,12,FIt is understood 24 Georgian and
OL,13,FIndian crew members remain on board
OL,14,Fand are assisting with the
OL,15,Finvestigation. The vessel Smyrtos
OL,16,Fremains at anchorage off the Dorset
OL,17,Fcoast.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
