PN,31704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1781608793
OL,3,CIndian national arrested after Russian
OL,4,Cshadow vessel intercepted in Channel
OL,6,FAccording to the MoD, the operation
OL,7,Fwas supported by aircraft from the
OL,8,FMaritime Air Group (Chinooks, Merlin
OL,9,FMk4 and Wildcat), an RAF P-8 aircraft,
OL,10,Fand HMS Sutherland and HMS Ledbury.
OL,12,FIn footage released by the MoD,
OL,13,Fpersonnel are shown boarding the
OL,14,Fvessel in the dark by fast-roping from
OL,15,Fa CH-47 Chinook helicopter.
OL,17,FFurther video clips show personnel
OL,18,Farmed with KS-1 rifles conducting
OL,19,Fsearches of cabins aboard the vessel,
OL,20,Fwhile officers from the NCA inspect
OL,21,Fdocumentation and paperwork.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
