PN,31705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1781608793
OL,3,CIndian national arrested after Russian
OL,4,Cshadow vessel intercepted in Channel
OL,6,FAccording to the MarineTraffic
OL,7,Fwebsite, Smyrtos sails under the
OL,8,FCameroon flag and left Ust-Luga,
OL,9,FRussia, on June 5, with Port Said,
OL,10,FEgypt, listed as its destination.
OL,12,FSir Keir Starmer said in a statement:
OL,13,F"This operation delivers yet another
OL,14,Fblow to Russia and reminds those
OL,15,Ffuelling (President Vladimir) Putin's
OL,16,Fwar in Ukraine that they cannot hide.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/14
