PN,31706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1781608793
OL,3,CIndian national arrested after Russian
OL,4,Cshadow vessel intercepted in Channel
OL,6,F"I want to pay tribute to all those
OL,7,Finvolved, including our armed forces
OL,8,Fand law enforcement officers who keep
OL,9,Fthis country safe 24 hours a day, 365
OL,10,Fdays a year."
OL,12,FSir Keir said in March that the UK
OL,13,Fwould join northern European allies in
OL,14,Fintercepting Russia's shadow fleet, in
OL,15,Fan attempt to "go after" the sanction-
OL,16,Fbreaking ships "even harder".
OL,18,FIt is understood Sunday's operation
OL,19,Fwas the result of months of planning.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@MO]wD@OOUwD@XO]xD@POUxD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/14
