OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1781608793
OL,3,CIndian national arrested after Russian
OL,4,Cshadow vessel intercepted in Channel
OL,6,FA Government source said: "This has
OL,7,Fbeen months in the making, with
OL,8,Fsignificant cross-government planning
OL,9,Fworking through the legal and
OL,10,Fpractical challenges.
OL,12,F"It is just the beginning and the
OL,13,FPrime Minister has made clear that
OL,14,FPutin will not win."
OL,26,@nD@[OUtD@AOUvD@TO]
