OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1781608793
OL,3,CIndian national arrested after Russian
OL,4,Cshadow vessel intercepted in Channel
OL,6,FMoscow's shadow fleet is reported to
OL,7,Fbe made up of more than a thousand
OL,8,Fageing tankers which illicitly ship
OL,9,Foil and other goods out of Russia by
OL,10,Fflying the flags of other countries,
OL,11,Fwith the aim of evading sanctions
OL,12,Fimposed by the West since the invasion
OL,13,Fof Ukraine began.
OL,15,FClosing off British waters to the
OL,16,Fshadow fleet is aimed at forcing the
OL,17,FRussian vessels into taking longer,
OL,18,Fmore costly sea routes, or risk being
OL,19,Fintercepted by the UK.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
