PN,31709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1781608793
OL,3,CIndian national arrested after Russian
OL,4,Cshadow vessel intercepted in Channel
OL,6,FBritish forces have already been
OL,7,Finvolved in tracking shadow fleet
OL,8,Fvessels for several years and have
OL,9,Fsupported operations by other
OL,10,Fcountries to seize the ships.
OL,12,FLord Dannatt, the former chief of the
OL,13,Fgeneral staff, said the interception
OL,14,Fcould result in Russian warships
OL,15,Fescorting tankers through UK waters in
OL,16,Ffuture.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
