PN,31710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1781608793
OL,3,CIndian national arrested after Russian
OL,4,Cshadow vessel intercepted in Channel
OL,6,FHe told GB News that one
OL,7,F"consideration is whether the Russians
OL,8,Fwill, now that they've seen that we're
OL,9,Fprepared to intercept these tankers in
OL,10,Fsomething like the English Channel,
OL,11,Fwhether they will start to escort with
OL,12,Fa Russian warship".
OL,14,FDefence Secretary Dan Jarvis said:
OL,15,F"Operations like this require skill,
OL,16,Fprofessionalism and courage.
OL,18,F"I pay tribute to our armed forces
OL,19,Fpersonnel and all those involved.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@RO]wD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/14
