PN,31711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1781608793
OL,3,CIndian national arrested after Russian
OL,4,Cshadow vessel intercepted in Channel
OL,6,F"Russia relies on its shadow fleet to
OL,7,Ffund their conflict in Ukraine and our
OL,8,Finterdiction delivers a blow to
OL,9,FPutin's illegal war."
OL,11,FAttorney General Lord Richard Hermer
OL,12,Fwrote on LinkedIn: "This Government
OL,13,Fmade clear that we would pursue
OL,14,FRussia's shadow fleet under the full
OL,15,Fforce of international law.
OL,17,F"Russia relies on their shadow fleet
OL,18,Ftankers to fund their conflict in
OL,19,FUkraine, and this expertly delivered
OL,20,Finterdiction strikes another blow at
OL,21,FPutin's war machine.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@UO]tD@TOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/14
