CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1781608793
OL,3,CIndian national arrested after Russian
OL,4,Cshadow vessel intercepted in Channel
OL,6,F"I pay tribute to the extraordinary
OL,7,Fcourage and professional of our armed
OL,8,Fforces personnel, and everyone else
OL,9,Finvolved."
OL,11,FTory leader Kemi Badenoch wrote on X:
OL,12,F"I pay tribute to the brave Royal
OL,13,FMarine Commandos who boarded a Russian
OL,14,Fshadow fleet oil tanker overnight in
OL,15,Fthe English Channel.
OL,17,F"Russia's illegal war in Ukraine is
OL,18,Ffunded by their oil exports in
OL,19,Fdefiance of sanctions.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@JO]tD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
