CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1781608793
OL,3,CIndian national arrested after Russian
OL,4,Cshadow vessel intercepted in Channel
OL,6,F"As Leader of the Opposition, I
OL,7,Fsupport the Government in standing
OL,8,Fwith Ukraine."
OL,10,FVolodymyr Zelensky thanked the UK for
OL,11,F"such principled resolve".
OL,13,FThe Ukrainian president wrote on X: "I
OL,14,Fam grateful to the UK for taking this
OL,15,Fimportant step against Russia's oil
OL,16,Ffleet ` a shadow fleet tanker has been
OL,17,Fdetained off the UK's southern coast.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@NO]sD@AOUsD@YO]uD@eOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
