PN,31714
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1781608793
OL,3,CIndian national arrested after Russian
OL,4,Cshadow vessel intercepted in Channel
OL,6,F"It was Russia's hubris, fuelled by
OL,7,Fhigh oil and gas revenues, that paved
OL,8,Fthe way for this war, and every
OL,9,Fdecision by partners that deprives
OL,10,FRussia of money also limits the war
OL,11,Fitself.
OL,13,F"I thank @Keir Starmer and all Britons
OL,14,Ffor such principled resolve. And
OL,15,FEurope urgently needs to take
OL,16,Flegislative steps to enable not only
OL,17,Fthe detention of tankers and
OL,18,Frestrictions on oil shipments, but
OL,19,Falso the confiscation of the oil they
OL,20,Fcarry. This will certainly help bring
OL,21,Fpeace closer."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUuD@Opo}D@NO]
